<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/objectives.css">

<section class="objectives-page" aria-label="Gate Keeper Objectives">
  <header class="objectives-header">
    <h1 class="objectives-title">Objectives</h1>
    <p class="objectives-tagline">Tap an item to view details.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="objectives-list">
    <details class="objective-card">
      <summary class="objective-summary">
        <div class="objective-summary-left">
          <img class="objective-thumb" src="/images/objectives/RemoteToBeacon.png" alt="Remote and beacon illustration" />
          <div class="objective-summary-text">
            <span class="objective-name">Fully automate gate opening and shutting</span>
            <span class="objective-short">Presence detection + state tracking</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="objective-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>

      <div class="objective-body">
        <ul class="objective-points">
          <li>Use Bluetooth beacons to detect the presence and absence of vehicles.</li>
          <li>Use limit switches to detect the physical state of the gate.</li>
          <li>Use programmable micro-controllers to act on varying conditions.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="objective-card">
      <summary class="objective-summary">
        <div class="objective-summary-left">
          <img class="objective-thumb" src="/images/objectives/ObstacleDetect.png" alt="Obstacle detection illustration" />
          <div class="objective-summary-text">
            <span class="objective-name">Obstacle detection safety</span>
            <span class="objective-short">Prevent closing when blocked</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="objective-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>

      <div class="objective-body">
        <ul class="objective-points">
          <li>Prevent the gate from shutting when an obstacle is detected.</li>
          <li>Open the gate if an obstacle is detected while shutting.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="objective-card">
      <summary class="objective-summary">
        <div class="objective-summary-left">
          <img class="objective-thumb" src="/images/objectives/ManualOverride.png" alt="Manual override illustration" />
          <div class="objective-summary-text">
            <span class="objective-name">Adapt to manual overrides</span>
            <span class="objective-short">Resume automation from the new state</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="objective-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>

      <div class="objective-body">
        <ul class="objective-points">
          <li>If a human operates the gate via app or remote, the system tracks the change.</li>
          <li>After manual operation, automated operations resume from the new state.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="objective-card">
      <summary class="objective-summary">
        <div class="objective-summary-left">
          <img class="objective-thumb" src="/images/objectives/ClockTimer.png" alt="Real-time clock module illustration" />
          <div class="objective-summary-text">
            <span class="objective-name">Scheduled operation</span>
            <span class="objective-short">RTC-based routines</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="objective-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>

      <div class="objective-body">
        <ul class="objective-points">
          <li>Keep the gate open for gardener and pool cleaner.</li>
          <li>Automatically adjust for daylight savings time.</li>
          <li>Sync with an internet-based clock for accuracy.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="objective-card">
      <summary class="objective-summary">
        <div class="objective-summary-left">
          <img class="objective-thumb" src="/images/objectives/SolarEnergy.png" alt="Solar energy illustration" />
          <div class="objective-summary-text">
            <span class="objective-name">100% solar powered</span>
            <span class="objective-short">Off-grid autonomy</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="objective-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>

      <div class="objective-body">
        <ul class="objective-points">
          <li>Minimum autonomy length of 5 days.</li>
          <li>Completely self-sustaining without power from the home.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="objective-card">
      <summary class="objective-summary">
        <div class="objective-summary-left">
          <img class="objective-thumb" src="/images/objectives/RainCloud.png" alt="Outdoor operation illustration" />
          <div class="objective-summary-text">
            <span class="objective-name">Continuous outdoor operation</span>
            <span class="objective-short">Weather-proofing requirements</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="objective-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>

      <div class="objective-body">
        <ul class="objective-points">
          <li>All electronics must be stored in a weather-proof container.</li>
          <li>All electrical connections must be weather-proof.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>
